Package: jointCPUE
Type: Package
Title: Joint Spatiotemporal CPUE Standardization Using TMB
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-11-26
Authors@R: 
    person("Rujia", "Bi", email = "bikayla5@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Rujia Bi [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Rujia Bi <bikayla5@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a joint framework for catch-per-unit-effort (CPUE)
    standardization using Template Model Builder (TMB). The package
    supports joint analysis of multiple fleets and spatiotemporal random
    fields via SPDE, with an initial application to neon flying squid in
    the NPFC Convention Area.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.4.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    Matrix,
    methods,
    stats,
    fmesher,
    TMB,
    sf
LinkingTo:
    RcppEigen,
    TMB
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/RujiaBi/jointCPUE
BugReports: https://github.com/RujiaBi/jointCPUE/issues
